________________________________________
Methodology Identified
This program followed a structured modernization methodology:
Lift – Transform – Optimize Model
1.	Lift: Automated migration
2.	Transform: Structural refactoring
3.	Optimize: Performance engineering
4.	Standardize: Governance
5.	Automate: DevOps integration
6.	Modernize: Platform engineering
This is a platform modernization methodology, not a simple migration model.
________________________________________
Lessons Learned
1.	Tool-based migration is only the starting point
2.	Post-migration engineering is critical
3.	Governance prevents technical debt
4.	Automation is mandatory for scale
5.	Databases are platforms, not just storage engines
6.	Cloud readiness must be designed
7.	Performance requires architectural alignment
